是对青桐高中指责VTuber春雨丽“经济困难”的回应不满吗？ https://p2y.jp/hakugei-hoeru-who-accused-vtuber-harusame-urame-of-money-trouble-expresses-dissatisfaction-with-the-response-from-aogiri-high-school/ https://p2y.jp/hakugei-hoeru-who-accused-vtuber-harusame-urame-of-money-trouble-expresses-dissatisfaction-with-the-response-from-aogiri-high-school/#respondp2y_admin Fri, 21 Jul 2023 02:49:51 +0000 VTuberバーチャルTwitterviviONYouTuberあおぎり高校バーチャルYouTuber個人勢春雨麗女白鯨ほえる https://p2y.jp/?p=96911 <p> VTuber Rei Harusame（所属机构：Aogiri 高中）被指控在私生活中存在“财务问题”。[...]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hakugei-hoeru-who-accused-vtuber-harusame-urame-of-money-trouble-expresses-dissatisfaction-with-the-response-from-aogiri-high-school/">VTuber Rei Harusame 指责“财务问题”白鲸咆哮青桐高中的帖子表示不满，该回复</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>被指控在<strong>VTuber春雨丽</strong>（所属：青桐高中）的私生活中存在“财务问题”的<strong>博艺Hoeru</strong> （独立）将于2023年7月19日加入春雨。他对此事的答复表示不满应该是青桐高中出身的。</p><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><em>我得到了回复。废话，结束</em></p><cite>@抽搐</cite></blockquote><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://twitter.com/hoeru_hakugei/status/1681603920333017089" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img data-attachment-id="96915" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hakugei-hoeru-who-accused-vtuber-harusame-urame-of-money-trouble-expresses-dissatisfaction-with-the-response-from-aogiri-high-school/hakugei_hoeru_who_accused_vtuber_harusame_urame_of_money_trouble_expresses_dissatisfaction_with_the_response_from_aogiri_high_school/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hakugei_hoeru_who_accused_vtuber_harusame_urame_of_money_trouble_expresses_dissatisfaction_with_the_response_from_aogiri_high_school.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_