ength&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="aogiri_high_school_confirms_money_trouble_slander_etc_against_vtuber_harusame_urame" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aogiri_high_school_confirms_money_trouble_slander_etc_against_vtuber_harusame_urame.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aogiri_high_school_confirms_money_trouble_slander_etc_against_vtuber_harusame_urame.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="674" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aogiri_high_school_confirms_money_trouble_slander_etc_against_vtuber_harusame_urame.png" alt="" class="wp-image-96381"/></a></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> 【注意】<br>经确认，本公司所属VTuber“Harusame Reijo”散布私下财务困难、诽谤诽谤等虚假内容。<br>关于这个事情，我们会考虑如何处理，包括采取法律措施。请不要基于猜测进行诽谤。</p><p></p><cite>青桐高中的管理</cite></blockquote><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://twitter.com/hoeru_hakugei/status/1679452699065188352" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc8a3esxmgcno-25uZo9MinWGXslRXYNX-OkaQBhu8M8WrevLoozb6fOireiJF7D7DoMIx66UzUfXPh8rPaTklvscR_LPOdDzZ8ilYLqjZrGsrtwRe9Kp8hPJljomo2UU3Ql5WOJb0CdRYkDl9tu_hl6=w1097-h914-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="oupxs64ba796b33ed9" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
